{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I didn't know how I am going to go about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember-- could have been on the 16th or 17th of October, I knew that I'm not going to go back to my uncle either because that wasn't safe.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I went out to Ujpest, I remember, of course, no yellow star, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had some papers from the Zionists, which I got, that I was Horvath Laszlo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was my name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And very coincidentally those papers were representing a, a, a non-Jewish boy of 17 years of age, younger than I, which was also very handy, because the non-Jewish 19-, 20-year-old boys have already been called in for military service, of course.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I somehow got hold of these papers-- I'm not sure how, but from Zionist origin-- that I became Horvath Laszlo from Bekescsaba, where [NON-ENGLISH], my auntie who became a lawyer-- whom I showed, showed you, can show you here-- got married.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, as a child, spent some very pleasant summer holidays there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew the area very, very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So on the-- with this Horvath Laszlo paper, I went out to Ujpest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, I remember, I-- on that night, I knocked on the door of my good Christian friend.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He died, meanwhile.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, it was end of October, about 8, 9 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I lived in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I entered, they had people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had just finished dinner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they realized, of course, straightaway that, that, you know, what predicament I am in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't ask too many questions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They invited me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What was dangerous that other people were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But fortunately, they were decent people also.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
